Sentencas: Layered cobalt oxide materials YBaCo3.4Al0.3Ga0.3O7+ delta (YBCAG33) and YBaCo3.2Al0.4Ga0.4O7+ delta (YBCAG44) were prepared and the electrical conductivity, the thermal expansion coefficient and electrochemical performance were investigated as potential cathode materials for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: Preparation, characterization, and electrochemical properties of YBaCo3.4Al0.3Ga0.3O7+δ and YBaCo3.2Al0.4Ga0.4O7+δ cathodes for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: The highest conductivity of 6.2 S cm(-1) is found for YBCAG33 at 900 degrees C in air.
Titulo: Preparation, characterization, and electrochemical properties of YBaCo3.4Al0.3Ga0.3O7+δ and YBaCo3.2Al0.4Ga0.4O7+δ cathodes for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: The average thermal expansion coefficients of YBCAG33 and YBCAG44 in the range of 30-850 degrees C are 9.3 x 10(-6) K-1 and 9.0 x 10(-6) K-1, respectively.
Titulo: Preparation, characterization, and electrochemical properties of YBaCo3.4Al0.3Ga0.3O7+δ and YBaCo3.2Al0.4Ga0.4O7+δ cathodes for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: The ASR value of YBCAG33 and YBCAG44 cathodes on LSGM electrolyte is as low as 0.080 Omega cm(2) and 0.120 Omega cm(2) at 800 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Preparation, characterization, and electrochemical properties of YBaCo3.4Al0.3Ga0.3O7+δ and YBaCo3.2Al0.4Ga0.4O7+δ cathodes for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: In an electrolyte-supported single test cell, the YBCAG33 cathode exhibited maximum power densities of 392, 292, 203, and 129 mW cm(-2) at 800, 750, 700, and 650 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Preparation, characterization, and electrochemical properties of YBaCo3.4Al0.3Ga0.3O7+δ and YBaCo3.2Al0.4Ga0.4O7+δ cathodes for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: Preliminary results demonstrated that the YBCAG33 can be a promising alternative cathode materials in IT-SOFCs in terms of electrochemical performance.
Titulo: Preparation, characterization, and electrochemical properties of YBaCo3.4Al0.3Ga0.3O7+δ and YBaCo3.2Al0.4Ga0.4O7+δ cathodes for IT-SOFCs
